channel.title: Client Error What does it mean?
channel.description:
Well I got a client base that looked good and tryed to connect to my "Demonscape V.3" Server the client is found at [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,399849.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,399849.0.html[/url] I got this error: [code] Error: T2 - 126,126,126 - 23,0,0 - 83,109,97,108,108,32,104,111,117,115,101,32,4 0,108,118,108,32,50,48,41,10,71,-1, [/code]
Anyone got any ideas what it means? Thanks in advanced!
~Code God of Rs~
